<item>
            <title>[ZOOKEEPER-273] Zookeeper c client build should not depend on CPPUNIT</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/ZOOKEEPER-273</link>
                <project id="12310801" key="ZOOKEEPER">ZooKeeper</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;One should be able to build Zookeeper C client libs on a machine without CPPUNIT installation.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;A simple fix is to remove from configure.ac the following line:&lt;br/&gt;
M_PATH_CPPUNIT(1.10.2)&lt;/p&gt;

</description>
                <environment></environment>
        <key id="12412431">ZOOKEEPER-273</key>
            <summary>Zookeeper c client build should not depend on CPPUNIT</summary>
